## Overview

This workspace contains Postman collections and requests for accessing and utilizing open data from **[{{ name }}]({{ home }})**. It features user-friendly APIs connecting to a diverse array of datasets, selected for their popularity and relevance, covering topics such as transportation, public safety, environment, and housing.

## Data Access (Socrata SODA API)
Primary data access is facilitated through the **Socrata Open Data API (SODA API)**, part of Tyler Technologies' [Data & Insights platform](https://www.tylertech.com/products/data-insights) (the platform often still referred to as Socrata). These APIs provide robust data discovery and querying capabilities.
* [SODA API Developer Portal](https://dev.socrata.com/)

## Metadata & Enhancements (HVDNet)
To complement the core data APIs, this workspace includes supplemental endpoints from the **[High-Value Data Network (HVDNet)](https://www.highvaluedata.net)**. These provide:
* Standards-based, machine-actionable metadata (in formats like Croissant, DCAT, DDI).
* Other specialized services to support the **[FAIR data principles](https://www.go-fair.org/fair-principles/)** (Findable, Accessible, Interoperable, Reusable).

These enhancements simplify data understanding and integration for developers, data scientists, and intelligent agents, significantly reducing data wrangling efforts and boosting productivity.

## Automation
The generation and maintenance of this workspace are automated using the Postman Toolkit and related packages from the **[Data Artifex](https://www.dataartifex.org)** open-source project, ensuring consistency and up-to-date resources.

